 扮工時間9-6<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新登記</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fgcnr.htm&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVN6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=a9a80f6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm</a><br />\n電子表格傳送門-&gt; <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C%29.pdf&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVN6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=752645af\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf</a><br />\n實體表格傳送門-&gt; 各區民政事務處<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.had.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcontact_us%2Fcomment_c.htm&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVN6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=a6b08f87\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm</a><br />\n或公共屋邨辦事處<br />\n<a href=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201901%2F29%2FP2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVN6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=03e39b16\" target=\"_blank\">http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf</a><br />\n或選舉事務處(香港灣仔港灣道25號海港中心10樓/九龍九龍灣展貿徑1號九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">交表</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fvrsubmit.htm&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVN6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=5b2c0310\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">如你持有有效的香港郵政或電子核證服務有限公司的電子核證（個人）證書 &lt;- 呢個基本冇人有，所以唔使試</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">免費傳真方法 </span></strong><br />\nHelloFax 免費黑白5張 / FAX.PLUS 免費黑白10張<br />\n<br />\n【教學】選民登記7月2日截止仲未搞？ 教你手機內3分鐘完成手續<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2Fvotersubmit%2Fsoftware%2Fandroid-app%2F&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVN6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=d6f4a237\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/</a><br />\n<br />\n[/麻煩大家幫手share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]"},{"pid":"41a43626c9c0aee794948832154558eb608cd273","tid":1254354,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T06:35:27.000Z","msg":"應對「致年青人」嘅最好方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1254107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1254107</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n支持！我地要攻陷偽文宣嘅方法<br />\n<br />\n係現實生活上用愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5109143870ed7557c4c1d0e2a48b0bf09b3b241","tid":1254354,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e57c7f213e5b97915ca028098dce7741270532d7","tid":1254354,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec52291d9f3a8657b6f520648cfc2881a06da4cd","tid":1254354,"uid":266969,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"quote":{"pid":"10deddf88c3111f34b6540aad10f42272b9abd83","tid":1254354,"uid":191926,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T05:55:12.000Z","msg":"其實有一個方法<br />\n<br />\n你雙親要你幫佢搞youtube果時<br />\n你幫佢登入埋 你個account<br />\n<br />\n咁班老人家多數唔識複雜的野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見封面有咩  就按咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T05:57:32.000Z","msg":"佢會見到一堆J片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"ci